Click on any phone numbers in Chrome and make calls with Twilio Flex. This click-to-dial extension recognizes any clicked phone number and sends the phone number to Twilio Flex to automatically make a call. It works with Seasalt.ai's Twilio Flex implementation SeaX: https://seax.seasalt.ai/

To learn more about it, book a demo here: https://meetings.hubspot.com/seasalt-ai/seasalt-meeting
